			<abstract label="Abstract">The Trio Beauty Salon Collection, 1935-2004, consists of five Hollinger boxes containing various records and mementos related to the Trio Beauty Salon of Harrisonburg, VA. These records span the years from 1938-2004, with the majority dating from the time the salon was open from 1938-1976. They include legal and financial documents, photographs, record books, and personal documents of the operators of the salon. The collection is arranged in four series: Legal Documents and Correspondence, Financial and Tax Statements, Financial Records, and Personal Records. </abstract>
